\f2\b0\fs24 \cf4 On the third day a wedding took place at Cana in Galilee.\'a0Jesus\'92 mother\'a0was there,\'a0
\f3\b\fs18 \super 2\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and Jesus and his disciples had also been invited to the wedding.\'a0\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you knew Jesus was in it would it change your mind about serving?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If we just think what we are doing is a job and not ministry then we miss the point\'85He is here.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs28 \cf0 1)  A desperation for His voice\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf4 \super 3\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When the wine was gone, Jesus\'92 mother said to him, \'93They have no more wine.\'94
\f3\b\fs18 \super 4\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Woman, why do you involve me?\'94\'a0Jesus replied.\'a0\'93My hour\'a0has not yet come.\'94\

\f3\b\fs18 \super 5\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub His mother said to the servants, \'93Do whatever he tells you.\'94\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The people who serve have this attitude\'85they do whatever He tells them too!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Illustration of a Angie and needing to grow because she is new to all this\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs28 \cf0 2)  A focus of what we have and not what we don\'92t\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf4 \super 6\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Nearby stood six stone water jars, the kind used by the Jews for ceremonial washing,\'a0each holding from twenty to thirty gallons.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f3\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus could have talked about not planning well or all the things they didn\'92t do right.  \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f2\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Instead of he focused on what they did have.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Empty vessel of pottery.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f3\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The greatest vessels for miracles in the churches we serve are the people we lead and serve with.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0 \cf2 Illustration of us changing everything because I kept hearing we need more people and as I looked I thought\'85we have plenty of people\'85we needed to quit looking external and look at what we already had.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs28 \cf0 3)  A front row to the miracles of God\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf4 \super 7\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Jesus said to the servants,\'a0\'93Fill the jars with water\'94; so they filled them to the brim.\

\f3\b\fs18 \super 8\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Then he told them,\'a0\'93Now draw some out and take it to the master of the banquet.\'94\
They did so,\'a0
\f3\b\fs18 \super 9\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and the master of the banquet tasted the water that had been turned into wine.\'a0He did not realize where it had come from, though the servants who had drawn the water knew. \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f3\b\fs28 \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Only the servants got to see the miracle\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Do you want to be there when the water turns into wine?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0 \cf2 Illustration of Candy Jam and how I had a friend who said it must have been awesome\'85and it was\'85but he didn\'92t see the miracle\'85he missed it!\uc0\u8232 Our 6 month old church probably just held the largest trunk or treat event this city has ever seen and guess what.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \'a0Then he called the bridegroom aside
\f3\b\fs18 \super  10\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and said, \'93Everyone brings out the choice wine first and then the cheaper wine after the guests have had too much to drink; but you have saved the best till now.\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
