\fs18 \cf4 \super 11\'a0
\f2\b0\fs24 \nosupersub What Jesus did here in Cana of Galilee was the first of the signs\'a0through which he revealed his glory;\'a0and his disciples believed in him.\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f3\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Where people see Jesus more clearly, they\'92ll follow Him more closely\
